<h2>
<span>Welcome to my website!</span>
</h2>

<p><strong>This website will house all the rules required to play the tabletop roleplaying game I am creating! Right now only the General, Skills, and Races pages are active. I would specifically like feedback on what you like about the navigation system :D</strong>
</p><br><p>The purpose of this game is to give players the freedom to create whatever type of character they want, and be able to play it effectively! There are no classes so characters are defined by their race, background traits, feats, themes, combat styles, combat and spellcasting abilities, and of course, their personality! There are virtually unlimited ways to customize your character! Because there is so much information to filter through, I will create a search database which you can use to quickly find the options you are looking for: <a href="something.html">-database has yet to be made-</a>
</p><p>The second goal of this game is to be more realistic and intuitive than other 
roleplaying games. Combat flows more smoothly, skills are more evenly and comprehensively 
laid out, and the weapons/armour system closely resembles real-world combat without 
being overly complicated.
</p><p>There is a grand world to explore, and lore (which is not on the site yet) which I 
encourage you to take a look at!
</p><p>If you are looking for a highly customizable game system with easy to learn 
rules, realistic mechanics, and an emphasis  on flexible gameplay, this is the game 
for you! All the rules are explained on this site, so have at it!
</p>

